gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Knicks 122, Nuggets 84
gameRecap.excerpt: The Knicks win their fifth straight game as they defeat the Nuggets, 122-84. OG Anunoby recorded 26 points and a season-high six steals for the Knicks, while Jalen Brunson added 21 points and four assists in the victory. Nikola Jokic tallied 31 points and 11 rebounds for the Nuggets in the losing effort. The Knicks improve to 28-17 on the season, while the Nuggets fall to 31-15.
